OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FWindy
OL,6,Fat the start of the week with showers
OL,7,For longer spells of rain. However,
OL,8,Ftemperatures will also start to rise,
OL,9,Fwith more settled weather likely later
OL,10,Fin the week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
